WEBVTT

00:00:00.039 --> 00:00:25.719
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.asia Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:01:04.640 --> 00:01:06.159
You've always been so secretive

00:01:06.159 --> 00:01:07.519
about wanting to do something big.

00:01:07.760 --> 00:01:08.599
What exactly is this big thing?

00:01:08.719 --> 00:01:10.519
I want to defeat the Seven Sins Demon Emperor.

00:01:11.959 --> 00:01:12.640
What did you say?

00:01:14.280 --> 00:01:16.079
Did this kid just

00:01:16.239 --> 00:01:17.359
get his head knocked by Lei Long?

00:01:18.319 --> 00:01:19.439
What makes you think you can defeat him?

00:01:19.920 --> 00:01:22.040
With just your puppet and the Annihilation Universe Staff?

00:01:22.239 --> 00:01:23.359
I know my own strength alone

00:01:23.359 --> 00:01:24.200
is far from enough.

00:01:24.359 --> 00:01:26.200
That's why I want to form a team.

00:01:27.359 --> 00:01:28.920
Even if you unite all of Primordial Continent

00:01:28.920 --> 00:01:29.879
and every sect,

00:01:30.040 --> 00:01:31.120
you still might not stand a chance.

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:33.400
You should know, the Seven Sins Demon Emperor

00:01:33.879 --> 00:01:35.640
has the power to destroy heaven and earth.

00:01:35.879 --> 00:01:36.519
So,

00:01:37.239 --> 00:01:39.319
you'll keep suffering under the Demon Emperor's oppression year after year.

00:01:39.760 --> 00:01:41.079
Offering a Sacred Maiden every year as tribute.

00:01:41.239 --> 00:01:42.840
You, Jun Wushang, with your legendary reputationâ€”

00:01:43.560 --> 00:01:44.200
what if,

00:01:44.560 --> 00:01:45.719
one day, the Demon Emperor names

00:01:46.200 --> 00:01:47.480
Miss Ye for the sacrifice?

00:01:48.400 --> 00:01:49.599
Would you just obey without resistance?

00:01:53.799 --> 00:01:54.799
Fine, fine, fine.

00:01:55.040 --> 00:01:55.920
You're so impressive.

00:01:56.079 --> 00:01:57.599
You're the hero who shakes the world,

00:01:57.760 --> 00:01:59.040
unmatched and peerless.

00:01:59.040 --> 00:02:00.200
Then go do it yourself.

00:02:00.200 --> 00:02:01.879
We little people won't join you.

00:02:01.879 --> 00:02:02.319
Come on.

00:02:02.319 --> 00:02:03.040
Take care, we're not seeing you off.

00:02:03.159 --> 00:02:03.640
Please.

00:02:04.079 --> 00:02:04.799
Father.

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:06.640
I think Young Master Lin is right.

00:02:07.840 --> 00:02:09.360
No matter how strong the Seven Sins Demon Emperor is,

00:02:09.599 --> 00:02:11.240
we shouldn't keep living under his oppression.

00:02:12.240 --> 00:02:12.879
Yue'er.

00:02:13.639 --> 00:02:14.680
You've been bewitched by him.

00:02:14.680 --> 00:02:15.719
He's clouded your mind.

00:02:16.400 --> 00:02:17.719
Come here, come to your father.

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:18.520
Yue'er.

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:25.080
Well, Lin Yue,

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:28.840
it's one thing you took our family heirloom,

00:02:29.439 --> 00:02:31.360
now you want to take my precious daughter too.

00:02:31.599 --> 00:02:32.599
What are you trying to do?

00:02:33.199 --> 00:02:34.319
City Lord, you've misunderstood.

00:02:34.639 --> 00:02:37.000
Actually, I've already had someone I love for a long time.

00:02:42.680 --> 00:02:44.479
That's great.

00:02:45.319 --> 00:02:47.039
Then please spare my daughter.

00:02:47.599 --> 00:02:48.639
What do you want to do?

00:02:49.240 --> 00:02:50.599
You can go by yourself.

00:02:51.199 --> 00:02:52.120
Yue'er, come here.

00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:53.520
Father.

00:02:54.360 --> 00:02:57.439
I'm following Young Master Lin to gain some experience.

00:02:57.960 --> 00:02:59.039
You surely don't want

00:02:59.159 --> 00:03:00.879
me to become a profligate son like Lei Zong, right?

00:03:01.280 --> 00:03:03.000
Alright, I'll listen to you.

00:03:03.400 --> 00:03:03.840
Look,

00:03:04.039 --> 00:03:05.159
you've just been through all this today.

00:03:05.159 --> 00:03:06.120
Such a mess.

00:03:06.400 --> 00:03:08.000
Rest well at home first.

00:03:08.280 --> 00:03:09.120
Once you've recovered,

00:03:09.120 --> 00:03:10.800
I'll personally take you to the Forget Immortal Sect.

00:03:11.199 --> 00:03:11.800
How does that sound?

00:03:12.240 --> 00:03:13.319
You're doing this again.

00:03:13.680 --> 00:03:14.719
Do you think I don't know?

00:03:15.159 --> 00:03:16.319
If I don't go out now,

00:03:16.439 --> 00:03:17.599
I'll never get out.

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:18.800
Yue'er.

00:03:19.039 --> 00:03:20.319
When have I ever lied to you?

00:03:21.199 --> 00:03:21.520
Come.

00:03:22.919 --> 00:03:23.680
Be good.

00:03:26.960 --> 00:03:27.520
Brother Lin.

00:03:28.120 --> 00:03:29.960
You were trapped by Lei Long and got into danger in the formation.

00:03:30.360 --> 00:03:31.240
I couldn't help you.

00:03:31.560 --> 00:03:32.759
If you ever need anything,

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:34.759
just come to Biluo Supreme Palace to find me.

00:03:35.719 --> 00:03:36.520
Brother Qin, you're too polite.

00:03:36.680 --> 00:03:37.719
It all happened so suddenly.

00:03:38.080 --> 00:03:40.000
Besides, I didn't want to drag you into it.

00:03:40.840 --> 00:03:41.560
No matter what,

00:03:42.080 --> 00:03:43.039
you got out safely,

00:03:43.240 --> 00:03:44.159
and obtained the divine weapon.

00:03:44.479 --> 00:03:45.360
That's a good outcome.

00:03:45.680 --> 00:03:46.360
Young Master Lin.

00:03:47.080 --> 00:03:48.759
Thank you for your care these days.

00:03:49.520 --> 00:03:51.639
I need to go back and reorganize the caravan.

00:03:52.159 --> 00:03:53.439
But your great kindness

00:03:54.120 --> 00:03:55.039
I will definitely repay.

00:03:55.560 --> 00:03:56.479
Miss Luo, don't say that.

00:03:57.639 --> 00:03:58.960
We have a long journey ahead.

00:03:59.280 --> 00:04:01.000
We'll surely meet again in the future.

00:04:02.360 --> 00:04:03.080
You two.

00:04:03.560 --> 00:04:04.560
Farewell for now.

00:04:06.159 --> 00:04:06.919
Until we meet again.

00:04:07.759 --> 00:04:08.599
Take care. Wait for me!

00:04:08.879 --> 00:04:09.599
Wait for me!

00:04:11.199 --> 00:04:12.240
Good thing I caught up.

00:04:13.159 --> 00:04:14.360
Why aren't you staying at home?

00:04:14.840 --> 00:04:15.479
Why did you come here?

00:04:15.800 --> 00:04:17.040
Why should I stay?

00:04:17.360 --> 00:04:19.079
As soon as I get home, my father locks me up.

00:04:19.680 --> 00:04:20.800
Then how did you get out?

00:04:21.160 --> 00:04:22.519
Of course, I defeated the guards.

00:04:22.600 --> 00:04:23.600
Then I climbed over the wall.

00:04:25.439 --> 00:04:27.399
This time, I'm definitely going to the Forget Immortal Sect with you.

00:04:27.399 --> 00:04:29.240
I want to improve my cultivation.

00:04:32.519 --> 00:04:33.279
Young Master Lin.

00:04:34.160 --> 00:04:35.000
Alright.

00:04:35.480 --> 00:04:36.160
But you have to promise me,

00:04:36.240 --> 00:04:37.199
if your father comes looking for you,

00:04:37.639 --> 00:04:38.399
you have to go back with him.

00:04:39.959 --> 00:04:40.639
We'll see when the time comes.

00:04:44.000 --> 00:04:44.759
Farewell for now.

00:04:51.199 --> 00:04:52.279
The Primordial Battle is about to begin.

00:04:52.879 --> 00:04:54.279
But Lin Yue still hasn't returned.

00:04:54.639 --> 00:04:55.680
Do you have any news about him?

00:04:57.319 --> 00:04:59.120
Did he run into trouble?

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:01.000
I believe in Lin Yue.

00:05:02.240 --> 00:05:04.079
No trouble can stop him.

00:05:05.560 --> 00:05:07.040
The Little Sacred King is back.

00:05:09.439 --> 00:05:10.920
Our Forget Immortal Sect's Elder Longlin,

00:05:11.040 --> 00:05:11.680
the muscular one,

00:05:12.600 --> 00:05:13.519
and the one who practices swordsmanship,

00:05:13.519 --> 00:05:14.199
called Jian Chi'er.

00:05:14.199 --> 00:05:14.959
He's very hardworking.

00:05:14.959 --> 00:05:15.759
But not very bright.

00:05:15.759 --> 00:05:16.240
Little Sacred King.

00:05:17.839 --> 00:05:18.680
My Heavenly Evolution Sword Technique

00:05:18.680 --> 00:05:19.959
has reached the twelfth form.

00:05:19.959 --> 00:05:20.600
Impressive.

00:05:20.800 --> 00:05:22.680
Let's spar together sometime.

00:05:23.240 --> 00:05:23.720
Lin.

00:05:26.879 --> 00:05:27.920
Who is this?

00:05:30.439 --> 00:05:31.040
Let me introduce.

00:05:31.399 --> 00:05:32.839
This is Ye Mingyue.

00:05:33.040 --> 00:05:34.160
From Night King City,

00:05:34.600 --> 00:05:36.480
the Young City Lord.

00:05:37.519 --> 00:05:38.879
I've long heard of the Forget Immortal Sect's reputation.

00:05:39.000 --> 00:05:40.160
I'm here with Lin Yue this time,

00:05:40.279 --> 00:05:41.600
mainly to improve my cultivation.

00:05:41.920 --> 00:05:43.720
Please take care of me, everyone.

00:05:48.120 --> 00:05:49.839
So many beauties here.

00:05:50.240 --> 00:05:51.920
It's overwhelming.

00:05:52.040 --> 00:05:53.360
Thinking about others,

00:05:53.839 --> 00:05:56.920
but not about me.

00:06:02.439 --> 00:06:04.240
You have to let me finish what I'm saying.

00:06:04.680 --> 00:06:05.759
Please watch the replay.

00:06:08.000 --> 00:06:09.079
It's been so long since we last met.

00:06:09.439 --> 00:06:10.319
Did you miss me?

00:06:11.720 --> 00:06:14.319
I think about you every day.

00:06:15.920 --> 00:06:17.279
But you,

00:06:17.800 --> 00:06:21.160
probably aren't thinking about me anymore, right?

00:06:21.600 --> 00:06:23.000
That's a misunderstanding.

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:25.879
Even though Night King City is full of beautiful women,

00:06:27.240 --> 00:06:28.040
I

00:06:28.319 --> 00:06:29.879
walk through the flowers

00:06:29.879 --> 00:06:30.959
without touching a single petal.

00:06:30.959 --> 00:06:32.279
I remain chaste and pure only for you.

00:06:32.279 --> 00:06:34.160
A lot of trouble came up at this auction.

00:06:34.720 --> 00:06:36.720
I've been so busy dealing with everything.

00:06:37.680 --> 00:06:39.560
All my time is spent thinking about you.

00:06:39.720 --> 00:06:40.600
How would I have time

00:06:40.839 --> 00:06:41.959
to think about anyone else?

00:06:43.519 --> 00:06:45.240
Then what's going on with Ye Mingyue?

00:06:46.680 --> 00:06:47.240
Her?

00:06:47.680 --> 00:06:48.879
She's the Young City Lord of Night King City.

00:06:49.160 --> 00:06:50.680
She can help us in the future

00:06:50.680 --> 00:06:52.160
to fight against the Seven Sins Demon Emperor.

00:06:53.639 --> 00:06:55.160
She's very useful, really useful.

00:06:56.560 --> 00:06:57.279
Little Sacred King,

00:06:58.839 --> 00:07:00.160
here are the lists from Crimson Sky Pavilion and Demon Sea

00:07:00.160 --> 00:07:01.279
for those participating in the Primordial Battle.

00:07:08.199 --> 00:07:10.399
Chixiao Pavilion and Demon Sea

00:07:10.680 --> 00:07:12.560
So quickly, more than a dozen

00:07:12.800 --> 00:07:14.680
Rotation Realm level five experts have appeared.

00:07:15.199 --> 00:07:16.480
Looks like this Primordial Battle

00:07:16.639 --> 00:07:18.639
is much more interesting than I thought.

00:07:18.959 --> 00:07:19.759
I didn't expect

00:07:20.439 --> 00:07:22.480
even with the blessing of the Supreme Clear Pool,

00:07:22.920 --> 00:07:24.199
we're still a step behind.

00:07:27.040 --> 00:07:29.439
I have a question.

00:07:29.439 --> 00:07:31.000
I'm not sure if I should ask.

00:07:31.279 --> 00:07:32.360
Then don't ask.

00:07:35.079 --> 00:07:37.000
Since our strength is so different,

00:07:37.199 --> 00:07:40.199
why do we have to join this Primordial Battle?

00:07:41.560 --> 00:07:42.240
Ridiculous.

00:07:42.759 --> 00:07:43.560
If we win the Primordial Battle,

00:07:43.560 --> 00:07:46.000
we get a chance to enter the Secret Realm Dao River and cultivate Yaoki.

00:07:46.000 --> 00:07:47.199
It will strengthen our sect.

00:07:47.720 --> 00:07:50.160
Even if we lose, we gain experience and improve our cultivation.

00:07:50.839 --> 00:07:51.720
If we quit now,

00:07:51.720 --> 00:07:53.839
Wangxian Sect will lose its reputation.

00:07:54.079 --> 00:07:56.000
Elder Xuanyou still asks why we join.

00:07:56.000 --> 00:07:57.759
But if we know we'll lose,

00:07:57.759 --> 00:07:58.759
I don't think it's necessary.

00:07:58.759 --> 00:08:00.839
To gamble the sect's fortune.

00:08:00.839 --> 00:08:01.879
Just say it directly.

00:08:01.879 --> 00:08:03.160
Don't pretend it's for everyone.

00:08:03.160 --> 00:08:04.160
I've tolerated you for long enough.

00:08:04.160 --> 00:08:05.040
You big oaf.

00:08:05.240 --> 00:08:06.439
Don't think your muscles

00:08:06.439 --> 00:08:07.160
I... I...

00:08:07.160 --> 00:08:08.120
mean I can't beat you.

00:08:08.120 --> 00:08:08.800
Try me.

00:08:08.800 --> 00:08:09.959
Don't think your muscles

00:08:09.959 --> 00:08:11.120
make me afraid of you.

00:08:11.480 --> 00:08:12.160
Try me.

00:08:12.399 --> 00:08:12.879
I...

00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:13.879
Try me.

00:08:14.000 --> 00:08:14.560
Enough.

00:08:15.319 --> 00:08:16.240
That's enough from you.

00:08:18.920 --> 00:08:20.000
Let me be honest with everyone.

00:08:20.279 --> 00:08:21.439
I'm joining the Primordial Battle

00:08:21.920 --> 00:08:23.240
to go to Dao River

00:08:23.720 --> 00:08:24.800
and get the Brahma Fruit.

00:08:26.000 --> 00:08:27.519
Brahma Fruit.

00:08:28.120 --> 00:08:32.000
Dao River produces one Brahma Fruit every three thousand years.

00:08:32.519 --> 00:08:36.039
Legend says it can instantly raise cultivation to the Transcendence Realm.

00:08:36.320 --> 00:08:38.960
But Dao River only opens with great fortune.

00:08:39.759 --> 00:08:42.600
The Brahma Fruit is even more legendary.

00:08:42.759 --> 00:08:44.480
No one has ever seen it.

00:08:44.679 --> 00:08:45.480
Young Sacred King,

00:08:45.879 --> 00:08:48.759
are you sure you can get it?

00:08:49.000 --> 00:08:49.559
No.

00:08:50.000 --> 00:08:51.440
But it's my only way.

00:08:51.440 --> 00:08:52.840
I must join the Primordial Battle.

00:08:53.399 --> 00:08:55.559
Get the Brahma Fruit to increase my strength.

00:08:56.120 --> 00:08:58.120
Only then can I defeat the Seven Sins Demon Emperor.

00:08:59.879 --> 00:09:00.360
Seven...

00:09:01.320 --> 00:09:01.720
I...

00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:03.080
You... you...

00:09:04.840 --> 00:09:05.679
Young Sacred King,

00:09:06.039 --> 00:09:08.240
if I heard correctly,

00:09:08.399 --> 00:09:10.159
you're joining the Primordial Battle

00:09:10.480 --> 00:09:12.039
for the Brahma Fruit.

00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:14.320
And if you get the Brahma Fruit,

00:09:14.639 --> 00:09:16.919
it's to challenge the Seven Sins Demon Emperor.

00:09:17.039 --> 00:09:17.559
Yes.

00:09:19.120 --> 00:09:20.720
Our sect's Sacred Maiden Qin Yiyi

00:09:21.440 --> 00:09:23.279
won't have to join the Demon Emperor's sacrifice anymore.

00:09:24.360 --> 00:09:25.399
Sect Leader,

00:09:25.679 --> 00:09:26.360
you... you...

00:09:26.519 --> 00:09:27.919
You've known about this all along?

00:09:30.799 --> 00:09:31.480
Crazy.

00:09:32.320 --> 00:09:33.679
This is truly crazy.

00:09:35.759 --> 00:09:36.639
Young Sacred King,

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:40.360
Forgive me, I'm old and weak, my power is low.

00:09:40.360 --> 00:09:42.919
I won't go with you this time.

00:09:45.600 --> 00:09:46.919
This is madness.

00:09:48.639 --> 00:09:51.440
Go to the Primordial Battle for the Brahma Fruit,

00:09:52.240 --> 00:09:53.559
defeat the Seven Sins Demon Emperor...

00:09:54.399 --> 00:09:55.000
I know,

00:09:55.720 --> 00:09:57.679
it all sounds like a fairy tale.

00:09:58.039 --> 00:09:59.440
If you don't want to believe me,

00:10:00.200 --> 00:10:01.000
I won't force you.

00:10:02.159 --> 00:10:02.919
Young Sacred King,

00:10:03.120 --> 00:10:04.960
I, Longlin, am not one to fear death.

00:10:05.519 --> 00:10:06.840
But this concerns the sect.

00:10:07.600 --> 00:10:08.360
We can't act recklessly.

00:10:10.279 --> 00:10:10.960
Young Sacred King,

00:10:12.120 --> 00:10:13.600
I need to think it over.

00:10:19.840 --> 00:10:21.600
I thought after you returned from Night King City,

00:10:22.759 --> 00:10:24.120
you wouldn't mention this again.

00:10:24.639 --> 00:10:25.720
You underestimate me.

00:10:26.399 --> 00:10:27.759
I don't care if you go or not.

00:10:28.759 --> 00:10:29.600
The Brahma Fruit

00:10:29.960 --> 00:10:30.639
is mine for sure.

00:10:31.000 --> 00:10:32.320
To oppose the Demon Emperor

00:10:33.399 --> 00:10:35.480
will put the sect in danger.

00:10:37.679 --> 00:10:39.600
Don't forget our agreement.